                    </div2>
                    <div2>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b01"/>熙平二年太歲在丁酉三月<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">丙</unclear>酉朔□日壬戌
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b02"/>　比丘劉僧<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">真</unclear>少□道門。志□於外。□□□累
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b03"/>　<note n="0043001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03567;＝劫【中研院】</note><app n="0043001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03567;</rdg></app>之苦。□□有在□□緣以□□□□□□ 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b04"/>　臨高照之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">隆</unclear>□。並四時□□□□□樂逾□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b05"/>天宮。供施精巖。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">使</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">外</unclear>□万路歸□。道俗恭□連
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b06"/>車蓋疋興逮。上為皇帝延綿。師僧先<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">妣</unclear>。造石像
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b07"/>一<note n="0043002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00502;＝軀【中研院】</note><app n="0043002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">軀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00502;</rdg></app>。興福以誌。願皇帝隆綿。師僧父母。朗朗與
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b08"/>三光並暈。覆則与乾<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">晨</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">同</unclear>□。下為四部道俗欽
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b09"/>明。核業藏潤。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">宿</unclear>信<note n="0043003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30394;＝彌【中研院】</note><app n="0043003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app>樂。敬崇三寶。□智龍天。任
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b10"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">顥</unclear>皇朝有類氏人女□□□外渡四&CB00515;。除充主
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b11"/>公<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">郡</unclear>想。競業疇延。室家和望。眾陳天<note n="0043004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08832;＝算【中研院】</note><app n="0043004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">算</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08832;</rdg></app>正始<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">智</unclear>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b12"/>然合邑子等。閻石記<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">念</unclear>。永世留名。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">為</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">恐</unclear>事記願
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b13"/>登覽首。未<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">來</unclear>世中。彌勒三會。□等蓋□。願願從
                            <lb ed="I" n="0043b14"/>心。三有群生。普同成佛。
